Unitron descended rapidly and transformed to his biped form in mid air, 
crashing into the ground feet first, staying on his feet easily.

"This is it, eh?" he said as he saw the Dark Avian and showing no signs of 
caring.  "Well, take me to the so-called Megatron immediately.  I have more 
important matters to attend to."
